{{Transcript list|Kaqemeex|Thordur|Druid}}

==Starting the event==
* '''Player:''' Hello there.
* '''Player:''' What are you doing?
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Ah, some help. Every year around this time of year, we druids perform a ritual to protect nature from evil corrupting spirits.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' But this year, our ritual doesn't seem to be working. Try as we might, the Altar of Guthix isn't responding to us.
* '''Player:''' Is there anything I can do to help?
* '''Kaqemeex:''' If you could join in with our chant, we might see some progress.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Gather around the altar and chant when you are ready.
* {{tact|end}}

===Chanting at the [[Altar of Guthix]]===
* '''Player:''' {{overhead|Magtajkex, Hajexgrace, Hexjjagnoc, Gehaxjas, Rajflexaged, Waxhagjete, Negjaanorx}}
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Wh...what, it didn't work?
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Let me study this, come back to me in a bit.
* {{tact|end}}

===Back in a bit===
* '''Player:''' Hello there.
* '''Player:''' What should we do know?
* '''Kaqemeex:''' I have a friend, a very wise old Dwarf, who might know what is wrong. Unfortunately, I can't leave the altar at such a critical time. May I ask you consult him on our behalf?
* '''Player:''' Sure.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Excellent. His name is Thordur.
* '''Player:''' How do I go about finding him?
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Thordur likes to hide between the planes of acceptance{{sic}}. You will not find him using convential{{sic}} adventuring. Thankfully, I can teleport you directly too{{sic}} him.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Ready?
* {{tselect|Do you want to go now?}}
* {{topt|Yes}}
** '''Player:''' Yes.
** '''Kaqemeex:''' Here we go.
** {{qact|The player is teleport to Thordur's blackhole.}}
* {{topt|No}}
** {{tmissing}}

===Talking to Thordur===
* '''Thordur:''' Welcome to Blackhole, human. Can I help you?
* {{tselect|What would you like to say?}}
* {{topt|Who are you?|event=no}}
* {{topt|What is this place?|event=no}}
* {{topt|How can I leave?|event=no}}
* {{topt|I'm fine, thanks.|event=no}}
* {{topt|Kaqemeex's business.}}
** '''Player:''' Kaqemeex sent me. He and the druids are having trouble with their ritual. The altar isn't responding to their chants.
** '''Thordur:''' Sigh...
** '''Player:''' What?
** '''Thordur:''' Were any offerings made to the altar?
** '''Player:''' Not that I'm aware of.
** '''Thordur:''' This happens every year....
** '''Thordur:''' .........hear that?
** '''Player:''' I hear something, it sounds very faint.
** '''Thordur:''' Those are voices; a spoken riddle. Solving the riddle will tell you what you need to offer to the altar in order for the ritual to work.
** '''Thordur:''' Listen carefully...
** {{tbox|You listen carefully and hear the following...}} ''A riddle is provided depending on the day, a full list can be found [[2014_Midsummer_event#Riddles|here]].''
** '''Player:''' I shall let Kaqemeex know. Thank you, Thordur.
** '''Thordur:''' Here, have this. It will get you out.
** {{tbox|pic=Disk_of_returning_detail.png|Thordur hands you a disk of returning.}}
** '''Player:''' Thank you.
** {{tact|end}}

===Returning to Kaqemeex===
* '''Player:''' Hello there.
* '''Player:''' Thordur told me that we need to make an offering to the altar. We need to decypher{{sic}} the item required from the riddle.
* ''A riddle is provided depending on the day, a full list can be found [[2014_Midsummer_event#Riddles|here]].''
* '''Kaqemeex:''' We forget about that every year.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' I hope you have your wits about you adventurer. These riddles are never easy and us druids are no good at them.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' If you can solve them for us, we'll reward you.
* {{tact|end}}

===Chanting at the Altar of Guthix with the answer to the riddle in your inventory===
* '''Player:''' {{overhead|Magtajkex, Hajexgrace, Hexjjagnoc, Gehaxjas, Rajflexaged, Waxhagjete, Negjaanorx}}
* {{qact|The chant is a success.}}

===Talking to Kaqemeex again===
* '''Player:''' Hello there.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' I saw it work! Well done!
* '''Player:''' Oh it was nothing really. Really easy, no problem at all.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Good, because this ritual will need to be repeated tomorrow.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' If you manage to do this three times for us, we'll give you a special reward.
* '''Kaqemeex:''' In the mean time, have this.
*{{tbox|pic=Half_full_wine_jug_detail.png|Kaqemeex gives you a half full wine jug.}}
* '''Kaqemeex:''' Just remember, it's half full, not half empty!
* {{tact|end}}

